title: What we know about Russia's interest in the seized oil tanker linked to Venezuela

description: Silver's spot price is just the starting point. Premiums, dealer fees and the product form all impact cost.
title: How much should you pay for 1 ounce of silver right now?

description: Tom Homan, the Trump administration's border czar, spoke to CBS News about the deadly ICE shooting in Minneapolis. When asked if ICE uses excessive force, Homan said, "I haven't seen one...ICE officer found guilty of anything inappropriate." He added he's not involved in every arrest, but trusts ICE and border control agents.
title: Border czar says ICE agents not "found guilty of anything inappropriate" amid raids

description: An ICE officer fatally shot a woman in her car in Minneapolis on Wednesday. Video shows the woman appearing to back up her car as one agent attempts to open the driver's side door. As she begins to pull away, another officer fires through the windshield. Nicole Sganga spoke with witnesses about what happened. Warning: the video in this story may be disturbing for viewers.
title: Witness on fatal ICE shooting in Minneapolis: "We just watched a murder by our government"

description: Lawmakers are reacting to the shooting involving an ICE officer in Minneapolis, Minnesota, on Wednesday, where 37-year-old Renee Good was killed. CBS News' Nikole Killion reports.
title: Republicans, Democrats react to ICE fatal shooting in Minneapolis

description: The House is on track to approve a three-year extension of expired health care tax credits, with a growing number of Republicans poised to back the measure.
title: House poised to approve 3-year health care tax credit extension

description: Homeland Security Secretary Kristi Noem claimed Renee Good, the woman fatally shot by an ICE officer in Minneapolis during heated protests, had been harassing officers before the incident. CBS News' Nicole Sganga reports.
title: Noem claims Renee Good was stalking and harrassing ICE officers before she was killed

description: Protests erupt after a Minneapolis woman is killed by a federal immigration agent. Plus, the U.S. seizes two more oil tankers linked to Venezuela. All that and all that matters in today's Eye Opener.
title: Eye Opener: Woman shot and killed by ICE officer in Minneapolis

description: The United Kingdom aided the U.S. in an operation to seize a sanctioned oil tanker linked to Venezuela in the North Atlantic. CBS News' Ramy Inocencio reports.
title: British military helped the U.S. seize an oil tanker linked to Venezuela

description: A recent CBS News poll shows Americans are split on the Trump administration's operation to remove Nicolás Maduro from power in Venezuela. This comes as President Trump comments on the country's future. CBS News' Anthony Salvanto has more on the data.
title: New poll shows Americans are divided on Venezuela as Trump says oversight could last years

description: The Trump administration is reacting to the shooting in Minneapolis involving an ICE officer and 37-year-old Renee Good, a U.S. citizen, who was killed. CBS News' Ash-har Quraishi and Natalie Brand report. Also, Joe Tamburino, an attorney and legal analyst, joins CBS News with more.
title: Video shows moments before ICE officer fatally shoots Renee Good in Minneapolis
